oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Autumn Evening at the Feed and Grain
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Hatch Show Print (Firm); Metal photoplates;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color window card (orange and brown on white) announcing an autumn evening at the Feed and Grain featuring the work of the Hatch Show Print and other local artists, presented by the Tenfold Collective, at the Loveland Feed and Grain on November 7.
